name: Blended
description:
2400X3480 pixels. 2021
"Blended" is the word to describe this collaboration. In this collaboration, we bring together the differences to become harmony. We put aside our ego to become outstanding among the others.
We are not just blending the differences between us, we are also blending two different worlds together, the marine world and the land world. This represents that we unite two individuals with different work backgrounds. The one works with digital medium with digital painting as the main weapon, and the other works with traditional medium with line as its main strength.
